{"about_the_game":"Gritty, open-world, survival-crafting, zombie shooter, created by a solo developer in Unreal 5.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578450/extras/Headline_1.png?t=1729622664\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578450/extras/MULTI_LAYERED_SURVIVAL.gif?t=1729622664\" /><br>Master a web of interconnected survival systems by managing hunger, thirst, energy, stamina, and body temperature against ever-changing conditions. Scorching heat drains hydration and energy more rapidly, while sudden rainstorms and cold nights can plunge your body temperature to dangerously low levels.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578450/extras/Headline_2.png?t=1729622664\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578450/extras/THE_CHANGING_SEASONS.gif?t=1729622664\" /><br>Adapt to changing seasons\u2014summer, autumn, winter, and spring\u2014each transforms the world with unique gameplay and visual changes. Plentiful but sweltering summers make foraging and hunting easier but test your ability to stay hydrated. Brutal winters demand more warmth and shelter but bring fewer zombie threats. Manage each season's shifting resources, weather conditions, and wildlife behavior.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578450/extras/Headline_3.png?t=1729622664\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578450/extras/EXPLORE_VAST_INFESTED_ISLAND.gif?t=1729622664\" /><br>Discover the rugged beauty of an open-world island inspired by the Pacific Northwest. Roam through dense forests teeming with wildlife, abandoned towns, and derelict farms as you uncover the dark conspiracy that brought you here.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578450/extras/Headline_4.png?t=1729622664\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578450/extras/SURVIVE_AND_THRIVE.gif?t=1729622664\" /><br>Hunt animals, forage for edible plants, and scavenge abandoned locations for resources. Build and upgrade bases, craft essential supplies, and loot what you can find. Find vehicles to explore further, but remember to keep them fueled. Maintain your weapons and clothing to stay ready for anything.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578450/extras/Headline_5.png?t=1729622664\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578450/extras/DEEP_COMBAT_SYSTEM.gif?t=1729622664\" /><br>Switch between ranged and melee combat to suit your playstyle. Choose from a variety of firearms to mow down zombies or get up close and personal with melee weapons or even your fists. Whether you prefer stealth, brawling, or sharpshooting, the choice is yours.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578450/extras/Headline_6.png?t=1729622664\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578450/extras/DYNAMIC_CAMERA_TECH.gif?t=1729622664\" /><br>A dynamic camera seamlessly transitions between two perspectives: a top-down view to explore, scavenge, and build with a clear view of your surroundings, and an over-the-shoulder view for enhanced weapon control and up-close combat when action erupts.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578450/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729622664","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578450/page.bg.jpg?t=1729622664","capsule_image":"https:/